Package scheduler

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cache
    Cache class is used for caching system.
    LFUCache
    LFUCache implements a less frequency used cache policy.
    LRUCache
    LRUCache class implements a cache policy where the last recently used process will be replaced when the cache is full.
    NoCache
    NoCache class does not implement any caching mechanism.
    ProcessCached
    ProcessCached is a class which encapsulates the process and its value in one variable.
    ProcessScheduler
    ProcessScheduler class is an abstract class which manages the processes by a given scheduler type.
    RandomScheduler
    RandomScheduler class implements a random scheduler where processes are chosen randomly.
    RoundRobinScheduler
    RoundRobinScheduler class implements a Round Robin Scheduler where the PID (the index in process list) is generated by applying modulo number of processes to the index of current input.
    WeightedScheduler
    WeightedScheduler class implements a weighted scheduler where any process is run by a given weight.
